# Rust Project Rules

## Tech Stack
- Rust (latest stable)
- Axum or Actix-web
- SQLx for database
- Tokio runtime

## Commands
- `cargo run` - Start server
- `cargo test` - Run tests
- `cargo clippy` - Lint
- `cargo fmt` - Format
- `sqlx migrate run` - Migrations

## Code Style
- No `unsafe` unless absolutely necessary
- Use `thiserror` for custom errors
- Prefer `impl Trait` over `dyn Trait`
- Document public APIs with `///`

